summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 35E, page 101 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone the property located at 1100 Denny Way from Neighborhood Commercial 3 with a 125 - foot height limit (NC3/125'), to Commercial 2 with a 125 foot height limit (C2/125') and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of The Seattle Times Company, C.F. 300224, Appl. 99402336)
